Get Migratory Survival Rates

get_migratory_survival.Rd

Calculates the juvenile out migration survival rates in all regions for a month and year of the simulation

get_migratory_survival(
  year,
  month,
  cc_gates_prop_days_closed,
  freeport_flows,
  vernalis_flows,
  stockton_flows,
  vernalis_temps,
  prisoners_point_temps,
  CVP_exports,
  SWP_exports,
  upper_sacramento_flows,
  delta_inflow,
  avg_temp_delta,
  avg_temp,
  delta_proportion_diverted,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_intercept_one,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_intercept_two,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_intercept_three,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_delta_flow,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_avg_temp,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_perc_diversions,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_medium,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_large,
  ..surv_juv_outmigration_sj_int,
  ..surv_juv_outmigration_sac_int_one,
  ..surv_juv_outmigration_sac_prop_diversions,
  ..surv_juv_outmigration_sac_total_diversions,
  ..surv_juv_outmigration_sac_int_two,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin_medium,
  .surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin_large,
  min_survival_rate,
  surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_model_weights
)

Arguments

year

The simulation year, 1-20
month

The simulation month, 1-8
cc_gates_prop_days_closed

More details at delta_cross_channel_closed
freeport_flows

More details at freeport_flow
vernalis_flows

More details at vernalis_flow
stockton_flows

More details at stockton_flow
vernalis_temps

More details at vernalis_temperature
prisoners_point_temps

More details at prisoners_point_temperature
CVP_exports

More details at cvp_exports
SWP_exports

More details at swp_exports
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_intercept_one

Intercept surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta for model one
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_intercept_two

Intercept surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta for model two
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_intercept_three

Intercept surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta for model three
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_delta_flow

Coefficient surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta for delta_flow variable
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_avg_temp

Coefficient surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta for avg_temp variable
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_perc_diversions

Coefficient surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta for perc_diversions variable
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_medium

Size related intercept for surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta medium sized fish
.surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_large

Size related intercept for surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta large sized fish
..surv_juv_outmigration_sj_int

Intercept for surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin
.surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin_medium

Size related intercept for surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin medium sized fish
.surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin_large

Size related intercept for surv_juv_outmigration_san_joaquin large sized fish
min_survival_rate

estimated survival rate if temperature threshold is exceeded
surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta_model_weights

weights for competing models
